title: Looks like someone’s mocking through someone with the Indian Trade Policies
selftext:
No Proposal Made: MEA Rejects Maldives Minister’s Claim on FTA

The recent romance between China & Maldives. The recent removal of Indian Defense forces from the islands, officially, then this. It’s clear that someone’s toying around with the already dented trade policies of our country. This is just a beginning of trade war, maybe?
